---
import { ArrowUp } from 'lucide-react';
---

<footer class="border-t border-border bg-foreground text-background">
  <div class="container mx-auto grid gap-8 px-4 py-14 md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] md:items-center md:py-16">
    <div>
      <a href="#top" class="inline-flex items-center gap-4" aria-label="有限会社板橋石材 ホームへ">
        <img src="/logo.svg" alt="" class="size-14 shrink-0 rounded-sm bg-background" width="56" height="56" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
        <span>
          <span class="block font-serif-jp text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[0.16em]">有限会社板橋石材</span>
          <span class="mt-1 block text-base tracking-[0.14em] text-background/68">宮城県大崎市鹿島台の石材店</span>
        </span>
      </a>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-base leading-8 text-background/78">墓石の新設・建て替え・リフォーム・追加彫刻・クリーニング・改葬まで、地域のお墓まわりを丁寧にお手伝いします。</p>
    </div>
    <a href="#top" class="inline-grid size-16 place-items-center justify-self-end rounded-full border border-background/20 bg-background/8 text-background transition-colors hover:bg-background/14" aria-label="トップへ戻る">
      <ArrowUp className="size-8" aria-hidden="true" />
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="border-t border-background/10 py-4 text-center text-sm text-background/58">
    © 有限会社板橋石材
  </div>
</footer>
